<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>

<activity xml:id="act-estrategiasRestar" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ol>
      <li>215. Sample response. I made 428 with the base-ten blocks. Then I took away 2 hundreds, 1 ten, and 3 ones. The blocks I had left showed 215.</li>
      <li>107: Sample response: I subtracted <m>505 - 400</m> because 398 is so close to 400. This gave me 105. I had to give 2 back though because I was only subtracting 398, not 400. This made the answer 107.</li>
      <li>267: Sample responses: <m>127 + 3 = 130</m><m>130 + 70 = 200</m><m>200 + 100 = 300</m><m>300 + 90 = 390</m><m>390 + 4 = 394</m><m>3 + 70 + 100 + 90 + 4 = 3 + 160 + 100 + 4 = 267</m></li>
    </ol>
  </solution>


